      <title>第一季進口抑制美國經濟，通膨加劇</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-economic-growth-slows-more-than-expected-first-quarter-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由於進口激增和企業未售出商品小幅增加，美國經濟第一季成長速度為近兩年來最慢，需求強勁的跡象加上通膨加速加劇了聯準會不會採取行動的預期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-economic-growth-slows-more-than-expected-first-quarter-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:37:28 GMT</pubDate>
